{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@discardableResult","kind":"attribute"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"onNotifyClosed"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ConnectFlags"},{"kind":"text","text":" = ConnectFlags(0), "},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO17DBusConnectionRefV","text":"DBusConnectionRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ParamSpecRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Void"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"flags","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Flags"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The signal handler to call","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Run the given callback whenever the "},{"code":"notifyClosed","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" signal is emitted"}]}],"name":"handler"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that getting this signal doesn’t itself guarantee that the value of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the property has actually changed. When it is emitted is determined by the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"derived GObject class. If the implementor did not create the property with"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then any call to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_set_property()"},{"text":" results","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"in ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"type":"text","text":" being emitted, even if the new value is the same as the old."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If they did pass [explicit_notify](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/explicit_notify, then this signal is emitted only"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when they explicitly call ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_notify()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_notify_by_pspec()"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and common practice is to do that only when the value has actually changed.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This signal is typically used to obtain change notification for a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"single property, by specifying the property name as a detail in the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_signal_connect()"},{"type":"text","text":" call, like this:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"(C Language Example):","type":"text"}]},{"code":["g_signal_connect (text_view->buffer, \"notify::paste-target-list\",","                  G_CALLBACK (gtk_text_view_target_list_notify),","                  text_view)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"C"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is important to note that you must use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"#class@GObject.ParamSpec#parameter-names"},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"detail strings for the notify signal."}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This represents the underlying "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify::closed"},{"type":"text","text":" signal"}]}],"style":"note","name":"Note","type":"aside"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The notify signal is emitted on an object when one of its properties has"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"its value set through "},{"code":"g_object_set_property()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_set()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", et al."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/dbusconnectionprotocol\/onnotifyclosed(flags:handler:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnectionProtocol\/onNotifyClosed(flags:handler:)"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"title":"onNotifyClosed(flags:handler:)","role":"symbol","extendedModule":"GIO","externalID":"s:3GIO22DBusConnectionProtocolPAAE14onNotifyClosed5flags7handlerSi10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV_yAA0bC3RefV_AG09ParamSpecN0VtctF","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"onNotifyClosed","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"flags"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ConnectFlagsV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ConnectFlags"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"handler","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"DBusConnectionRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO17DBusConnectionRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ParamSpecRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject12ParamSpecRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"text":"Void","preciseIdentifier":"s:s4Voida","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")